# @gravity-ui/eslint-config/base

Low-level base config with core JS rules using the Babel parser. Does not include TypeScript or React rules. The top-level package entry point already includes this via composition.

## Usage

```js
import baseConfig from '@gravity-ui/eslint-config/base';

export default [
  ...baseConfig,
  {
    // ...other config
  },
];
```

